room_title: Escape room "Clara's Diary" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
room_description: Clara Morris has a diary. In it, she writes of her beloved fianc√©, Henry, as she waits for his return from war. As fate would have it, Henry was killed with a bullet to the heart. A telegram was sent to dear Clara but was never opened. She had already died of a broken heart. Clara still waits in the room for her true love. Find the telegram to unite these two souls.
